 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a1f945262bf57ce9cdaa8930ae16e74f4459fb","tid":1972462,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cf9ad858f5260338f7724fd87c72c72893678bb","tid":1972462,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"第一條唔關事，英文寫明Any person who at any public gathering acts in a disorderly manner for the purpose of preventing the transaction of the business for which the public gathering is called tgt or incites others so to act....<br />\n<br />\n即係你做嗰樣要係要以擾亂一個公眾聚集為目的，先關事，而另外public gathering要超過十個人，兩點都中唔到<br />\n<br />\n第二條文其實要激使他人破壞社會安寧，或者自己可能會破壞社會安寧，單純講粗口我就唔知入唔入到啦，咁剩返激使他人，除非佢開到口叫手足燒佢啫，唔係就咁講粗口無得激使架喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"各被控一項在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序行為罪。案件今（14日）在東區裁判法院再訊，控方撤銷其中一項控罪，修訂另一項控罪為在公眾地方行為不檢罪<br />\n<br />\n我唸就係因為有機告得入先改控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab6891fc5460db72777fda093d36f3c4a32ab4e","tid":1972462,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3129734c90afb9d31fd8e8395030b84fc233e03d","tid":1972462,"uid":108016,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:54:48.000Z","msg":"叔一燒都有叫囂喎<br />\n幾時拉埋佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"佢本身響地鐵站打手足，請問比人吿未？警察唔執法就正義市民行私刑啦，呀 Sorry 警方先係全港最大私刑集團"},{"pid":"8e93ca8ea723f90758efb59c9ff804ba79420522","tid":1972462,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da4ea148151e4ef2bceda1d5178c914765e45ca7","tid":1972462,"uid":54517,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3129734c90afb9d31fd8e8395030b84fc233e03d","tid":1972462,"uid":108016,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:54:48.000Z","msg":"叔一燒都有叫囂喎<br />\n幾時拉埋佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"唔好再問點解唔拉呢個那個,因為d狗已經用咗半年有多去証明佢地係偏幫..........<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" c